  "html": "<h1>Metaverse Navigation Systems</h1>\n<div class=\"blocks\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">### OntologyBlock</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"metaverse-navigation-systems-ontology\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-4\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-5\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-6\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-7\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-8\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-9\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">owl:class:: mv:MetaverseNavigationSystems</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-10\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">owl:physicality:: ConceptualEntity</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-11\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">owl:role:: Concept</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-12\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-13\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Gaze-based and hand-tracked menus** for intuitive movement selection</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Spatial augmentation** inclu